  "bodyText": "MiniMax 2.7 & Kimi K2.5 are free on Zo Zo · Pricing About Newsletter Blog Resources Download Get started Back to Integrations Google Drive Access files in Google Drive, including Docs, Sheets, Slides, and Forms. Import, search, and work with your cloud documents. WHAT YOU CAN DO Search and import documents from Drive Export Google Docs as PDF or Word files Organize files and folders Share and manage file permissions Convert between Google Workspace formats TUTORIALS Productivity How to Use Google Drive with Zo Search, read, and manage your Google Drive files directly from Zo. Google Drive All Integrations Gmail Google Calendar Linear Notion Spotify Telegram X (Twitter) LinkedIn Dropbox Airtable GitHub Slack n8n VS Code Google Docs Google Sheets OneDrive Microsoft Outlook Figma Reddit PRODUCT Documentation Blog Newsletter Comparisons Pricing Skills Integrations Channels Models Product Updates INFORMATION FAQ Careers Brand Terms Privacy Help Center Contact Security COMMUNITY Discord LinkedIn X @zocomputer YouTube Testimonials Ambassadors Merch Zo Computer Company"
